scripts.cover: nyc --reporter=lcov mocha --require intelli-espower-loader test/*.js && nyc report
scripts.generate-scaffolding: repo-tools generate all && repo-tools generate lib_samples_readme -l samples/ --config ../.cloud-repo-tools.json
scripts.samples-test: cd samples/ && npm link ../ && npm test && cd ../
scripts.all-test: npm test && npm run system-test && npm run samples-test
